<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.7">
<l>piṇṭat tiraḷaiyum pēykkiṭṭa nīrccōṟum</l>
<l>uṇṭaṟku vēṇṭinī yōṭit tiriyātē</l>
<l>yaṇṭat tamarar perumā ṉaḻakamar</l>
<l>vaṇṭot tiruṇṭakuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">māyavaṉ ṟaṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Caw! Caw! Without wandering, running around,</l>
<l rend="indent">desiring to eat the balls of rice and water-boiled rice</l>
<l rend="indent">that were left for the demons,</l>
<l>Comb the curly hair that is black like the bee</l>
<l>that suits the beauty of the Lord of the heavenly celestials.</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the culry hair of Māyavaṉ!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
